My one pet peeve, is when people send me a tell for a a buff when we are pulling a monster that will just AE again and wipe c5 off them again, hi trash in Txevu.  I didnt really experince this in full force till last night, god I didnt realize how much it could piss me off.  Not to mention I would end up rebuffing the same group twice, because someone didnt get the ae cured and c5 bounced.
