                        <tr>
                                <td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">In group there is normally no problem with buffing.
<br />
It wears off, you recast.
<br />
Even if you buff someone which got rezzed, you cast group buff, so all are on same timer again.
<br />

<br />
As for raid, there is no way you can keep up. You get so many requests, that your timer is the same as the last one you buffed.
<br />
You know more or less when it will be off and one of our chanters MGBs haste/C5.
<br />
As for god, normally I just cast god on peeps asking.
<br />
People normally tell us after ez if we don't see them getting rezzed and then we buff em.
<br />

<br />
So I am also one of the persons which doesn't time each spell.</span><span class="postbody"><br />_________________<br />Iueamil
<br />
<a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=673580" target="_blank" class="postlink">Mah stuff</a>
<br />
<img src="http://www.neallj.btinternet.co.uk/iueasigglowVS.jpg" border="0" /></span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
